{"tid":1434723,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"關於衝機場，有幾樣野想你地諗下","createTime":"2019-08-09T00:46:27.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-09T02:35:02.000Z","uid":270170,"like":13,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"f53660c09be68be9ee20e87f8cff3df5ef1fa72d","tid":1434723,"uid":270170,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T00:46:27.000Z","msg":"話說呢兩日又有好多post出黎話搞鳩機場，為左鼓吹獨立思考，以下有幾點唔該大家諗諗佢先。<br />\n<br />\n簡單黎講，就係要問衝機場個<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">目的</span></span>係乜！<br />\n<br />\n1. 如果係要外國輿論支持香港，咁搞鳩機場就一定唔得。機場係好多歐洲國家心目中係神聖不可侵犯，搞鳩佢就當你恐襲。<br />\n<br />\n2. 但如果係要攬炒要外國驚左香港，即管去啦。但問心，攬炒巴做咁多野幫我地爭取外國支持，點解要同攬炒巴攬炒<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n3. 最重要一樣野，係我留意到好多所謂支持港獨既人話要搞鳩機場。利申我就支持最終要港獨，但你搞到全世界都驚鳩左你，第時邊個同你外交邊個承認你政權？<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">港獨唔係只得香港，而係最終以國家身分同全世界連結，唔洗再靠老共！</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"35bc2602ba15b1af319d75c48624d594c3bbab6a","tid":1434723,"uid":270170,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T00:49:03.000Z","msg":"自推十次"},{"pid":"a1586beebebe70a7a05e29bd8cb9db609c1ad254","tid":1434723,"uid":270170,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T00:50:16.000Z","msg":"倒數第9次 負皮比理由"},{"pid":"a35c73d7360ebf16bd1cc23de1b49b99cdd902b4","tid":1434723,"uid":270170,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T00:51:30.000Z","msg":"8"},{"pid":"3d29fe3a9b3426505f169176b3182def33617eaa","tid":1434723,"uid":76680,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T00:52:11.000Z","msg":"由頭到尾都冇人話衝機場喎"},{"pid":"1ff914ad1242f28e5968d79c4f2780e25df8d1de","tid":1434723,"uid":270170,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3d29fe3a9b3426505f169176b3182def33617eaa","tid":1434723